{"tid":1610201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者會黑警所有話要調查而隱瞞既事實我地一定要同父母講清楚","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T16:46:58.000Z","uid":33123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"62b32f62493c2f734efab41fa941df62cb7e8813","tid":1610201,"uid":33123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:39:29.000Z","msg":"依家有哂報導 講到明中肺部 係心臟附近都可以話係要調查先可以確定到準確位置 班狗仲可以話係左膊頭附近<br />\n<br />\n黑警對心口開實彈未調查好就可以話係合情合理合法 但又話未調查好<br />\n<br />\n話俾人打到生命受就到威脅到要開真槍 咁一定有表面傷勢啦 但咁都話要查下 咁試問個威脅有幾嚴重？<br />\n<br />\n班狗就係想班藍絲想聽到佢地想聽到既資訊 對佢地不利就話要調查<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">大家一定要清清楚楚同老豆老母講佢地點解要咁做同埋真相係點！<br />\n</span><br />\n根本佢地所以記者會都係為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抺黑示威者而開</span></span>"},{"pid":"e2c1b081b4a40234dd9fa05f77cb297cc4dd1c2d","tid":1610201,"uid":33123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"b39a06e43b25f04ed94f4bd8a3a8afa78d96951e","tid":1610201,"uid":33123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:42:13.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"7fde92069b8ebb1c8d82c0d7e6c7349406b4e968","tid":1610201,"uid":33123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:45:38.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"2cfbf539af70fd0d1f599e35b9388addecc95f75","tid":1610201,"uid":33123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:45:51.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"e26beb392c9b08634196671aa3754c9e8e52a502","tid":1610201,"uid":33123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:46:06.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"a5b7fed0c4b46476482d6633455f9baf5de7e22f","tid":1610201,"uid":33123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"e8b32d144f25a5f9567927040e417444642555ee","tid":1610201,"uid":33123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:46:26.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"28adaf75d9334c7b5ef